name: I Wanna Duloxetine
description:
This is an aiwana game, if you dont know what those are you can look here: I Wanna Be The Guy Fangames (cwpat.me)

weird platformer i cobbled together in 6 or so months, it has an easier and harder difficulty. this game means a lot to me

credits are in the game's readme along with a lot of other info. i dont think you'll enjoy it that much but if you do that means a lot to me
